            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Mai<surplus>i</surplus>ae <lb n="2"/>aedem a solo fe<lb break="no" n="3"/>cit <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Arrius Pa<lb break="no" n="4"/>truitus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata, mit Flechtband gerahmt. Doppelte hedera am Ende von Z. 1.</p>
            </div>
